{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d0cb4d0afa","title":"非自杀（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"749a4755f7","index":0,"year":1919,"month":11,"day":1,"articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1913-1943卷）（1968年武汉版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"1968年武汉","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f451a0cd90","type":"paragraph","text":"之盛，无不可与之联，洁为同心。此节和森信中能言，子升亦有提及。我觉得创造特别环境，改造中国与世界的大业，断不是少数人可以包办的，希望我们七十几","index":0,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"ff386cce4b","type":"paragraph","text":"个人，人人注意及此。","index":1,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"ba2e79e3ef","type":"paragraph","text":"我的意见大略完了。开子升已回国到北京，不人可以面额。箭在法友再将我的意见加以批解，以期求得一个共同的决定。个人幸甚，学会幸甚。","index":2,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"6e36af5a9d","type":"paragraph","text":"弟毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"8d8544e3eb","type":"paragraph","text":"九年十二月一日","index":4,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"f4bb27f042","type":"paragraph","text":"文化书泄夜十二时给和森的信","index":5,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"69f55e89b9","type":"paragraph","text":"九二一年一月二十一日利森见：","index":6,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"5a230a5464","type":"paragraph","text":"来信子年底始由子升聘到。唯物史观是吾党哲学的根据，这是事实。不象唯理观之不能证实而容易被人播动。我固无研究，但我现在不承队无政府的原理是可以证实的原理，有很强固的理由。一个工厂的政治粗械（工厂分配管理等）与一个国的政治粗，与世界的政治组械，只有大小不同，没有性质不同。工团主义以国的政治租与工厂的政治粗异性，为为另一回事而举以属之另一种人，不是因为曲以冀萄且偷安，就是悬随不明事理之正。况乎尚有开得政权即不能发动革命不能保护革命不能完成革命在手段上又有十分必要的理由呢。你这一封信见地极当，我没有一个字不赞成。党一层陈仲甫先生等已在进行粗，出版物-层上海出的“共产党”，你处可得到，不愧“旗想解，”四字，（宣言即仲甫所为）。群情后报。","index":7,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"eaf74332ee","type":"paragraph","text":"弟泽东","index":8,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"15b3eec76d","type":"paragraph","text":"十年-月十-一日在城南非自杀（节录）","index":9,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"4ed9bf575e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九一九年十一月一日）","index":10,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"92b418824f","type":"paragraph","text":"·..反抗旧避，与其自杀而死，宁奋斗被杀而亡。为目","index":11,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"1fff451421","type":"paragraph","text":"吾人应主张与社会奋斗。的达不到，截腾决战，玉碎而亡，则天下之至刚至勇，而最足以印人脑府的了！","index":12,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"},{"id":"ecf6656ee4","type":"paragraph","text":"（原载长沙《大公报》，抄自《光辉的五四》中国责年H版社一九五九年）","index":13,"publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa"}],"page":{"id":"b8c2bdea39","publicationId":"dfdd6b56-5f4e-42e1-af94-ae2ab38cc0b4","articleId":"d0cb4d0afa","start":57,"end":57}}}},"__N_SSG":true}